{"route":{"route":"/page/7/","outputPath":"page/7/index.html","kind":"home","title":"Asutorufaのブログ - Page 7","language":"ja","params":{"page":"7"}},"description":"こんにちは","posts":[{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/暗影精灵更改efi启动顺序.md","route":"/posts/6683eff9/","abbrlink":"6683eff9","title":"暗影精灵更改efi启动顺序","date":"2018-06-23 11:43:40","updated":"2018-06-23 11:43:40","tags":["EFI","BIOS"],"categories":["Computer"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>–2019-04-22 更新–<br>\n<strong>最新版bios已经可以调整启动顺序了(<a href=\"#jump\">图在最下面</a>)</strong></p>\n<p>-------- 之 前 -------<br>\n暗影精灵安装完ubuntu之后只能开机按esc+f9进入ubuntu，否则会直接启动windows,虽然可以使用但及其不方便的说</p>\n<p>首先从ubuntu进入/boot/efi/EFI<br>\n<strong>备份windwos的启动文件</strong>（<strong>切记一定要备份，否则只能从pe重新建立windwos启动项</strong>）</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">cp</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> -arf</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> Microsoft</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> win10</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>将ubuntu的grubx64.efi替换掉EFI/Microsoft/Boot/bootmgfw.efi文件</p>\n","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"6683eff9","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/関西弁コレクション.md","route":"/posts/a4241e7/","abbrlink":"a4241e7","title":"関西弁コレクション","date":"2018-06-21 09:42:02","updated":"2025-09-06 09:42:02","tags":["関西弁"],"categories":["日本語"],"language":"ja","htmlLang":"ja","locale":"ja_JP","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"ja-JP","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>普段発見の関西弁ここで記録します。</p>\n<p>–<strong>2025年9月6日</strong>–</p>\n<p>ほな</p>\n<p>大阪弁の「ほな」は、「それでは」「では」「それじゃあ」「じゃあ」といった意味で、接続詞としても、別れ際の挨拶としても使われます。また、前後の文脈によって「それなら」といった意味で使われることもあり、非常に汎用性の高い言葉です。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>しばく</p>\n<p>「しばく」には、物を棒などで強く叩くという意味と、大阪弁で軽い飲食や遊びに行くことを指す用法があります。前者は文字通り暴力的な意味合いですが、後者は「茶しばく」（お茶する）のように、親しい間柄での軽い誘いや日常的な表現として使われ、本気で殴るつもりはありません。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>–<strong>2020年1月30日</strong>–<br>\nおらん とはどういう意味ですか?</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>文からするとその方は関西の人ですかね。おらんは方言で、「いない」という意味です。<br>\n例文：<em>俺も一緒やな 3年ぐらいはおらん。</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>–<strong>2019年2月1日</strong>–</p>\n<hr>\n<p>①関西弁の～ねんけど、～やねん、～ねんの意味を教えて下さい<br>\n②～ねやは～ですかの意味ですか？それ意外に意味、使い方等は有りますか？<br>\n③言葉の関西弁のアクセントを教えて下さい</p>\n<p>①・・・<br>\n～ねんけど ですけれど（〇〇なんですけれど）<br>\n～やねん、～ねん です（〇〇なんです）</p>\n<p>②・・・<br>\n～ねやは～（～やねん”わ”～ですね。）<br>\n〇○なんですよ。</p>\n<p>③・・・<br>\n～ねんけど（中中）<br>\n～やねん（高低）<br>\n～やねんわ～（高低中）</p>\n","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"a4241e7","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/JavaScript对字符串操作.md","route":"/posts/86cfa6a/","abbrlink":"86cfa6a","title":"JavaScript对字符串操作","date":"2018-03-24 23:17:58","updated":"2018-09-04 23:17:58","tags":["JavaScript","前端"],"categories":["JavaScript"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"86cfa6a","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/让win10的UWP应用走代理.md","route":"/posts/d22ffdb6/","abbrlink":"d22ffdb6","title":"让win10的UWP应用走代理","date":"2018-02-08 15:09:16","updated":"2020-03-01 15:09:16","tags":["Proxy"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<h2 id=\"原因\">原因</h2>\n<p>因为uwp应用的特殊性,即使使用proxifier和proxycap这种应用也无法让其走代理</p>\n<h2 id=\"现在可直接用windowsloopbackmanager\">现在可直接用WindowsLoopbackManager</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tiagonmas/Windows-Loopback-Exemption-Manager\">WindowsLoopbackManager</a></p>\n","moreAnchor":"more","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"d22ffdb6","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/c语言数组输出的另一种方法.md","route":"/posts/854ed6ec/","abbrlink":"854ed6ec","title":"c语言数组输出的另一种方法","date":"2017-12-10 10:39:54","updated":"2017-12-10 10:39:54","tags":["C"],"categories":["Program"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>今天看到这样一种写法,原文链接:<a href=\"http://blog.accut.cn/archives/173\">一个有趣的C语言程序</a></p>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-c\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">#include</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> &#x3C;stdio.h></span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> </span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">int</span><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">()</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    int</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> a </span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    int</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\"> x</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">5</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">]</span><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">{</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">1</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">2</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">3</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">4</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">5</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">};</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\">    printf</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">(</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">%d</span><span style=\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span><span style=\"color:#E36209;--shiki-dark:#FFAB70\">a</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">[x]);</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">    return</span><span style=\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\"> 0</span><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span style=\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"shiki code-block language-bash\"><code><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line